What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Serverless Architecture Market?



Market Analysis and Insights :

Global Serverless Architecture Market

The server less architecture market will reach at an estimated value of USD 57.92 billion by 2028 and grow at a CAGR of 28.90% in the forecast period of 2021 to 2028. Rise in the number of verticals utilizing distributed workloads acts as an essential factor driving the serverless architecture market.

Serverless architecture usually depend upon third- party services and is generally used to build and run applications and services without any need to manage infrastructure. There is no need to maintain any application, storage systems or databases. This is very useful as now the organization can focus on the product rather than worrying about the management and operation of servers. They are extensively used in industries such as telecommunications, retail, healthcare, government and others.

Rise in the adoption of cloud based application is a crucial factor accelerating the market growth, also increase in the demand to eliminate management of server, increase in the app development, rise in the demand and adoption of cloud- based applications, increase in the powerful advantage to streamline operations and increase in the digital-centric business model are the major factors among others boosting the serverless architecture market. Moreover, increase in the usage of edge computing with serverless, rise in the emergence of IoT applications and rise in the research and development activities in the market will further create new opportunities for serverless architecture market in the forecast period mentioned above.

However, increase in the problems associated with the security and rise in the architectural and operation issues are the major factors among others restraining the market growth, while cost-efficiency for long-running computation will further challenge the serverless architecture market in the forecast period mentioned above.

